Introducing the Kupocard Mini!

Until Thu., Dec. 6, 01:59 UTC


Introducing a new Kupocard type, the Kupocard Mini!

The Kupocard Mini will grant you Initial Gems and Daily Gems for 7 days! It will be here until Thu., Dec. 6, 01:59 UTC, and may be purchased up to six times, so don't miss your chance!

Read on for more details!

About the Kupocard Mini

  • Kupocard Mini
    　　　　Initial Gems: 800
    　　　　Daily Gems: 100 (for 7 days)
    　　　　Total: 1,500

Upon purchase, you will receive the Initial Gems immediately, and the Daily Gems will be sent to your Gift Box alongside your Daily Bonus from your next login, for a total of 7 logins.

After receiving the seventh Daily Gems, you can purchase another Kupocard Mini as long as it is within the campaign period. This means you can get up to six this month!

* These logins do not need to be consecutive for you to receive all 7 login bonuses.
* Login bonuses reset at 08:00 UTC.
* You can confirm how many logins remain on your Kupocard(s) by tapping on the "Kupocards" button on the Gifts screen.
